DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(1,10,1);
$c = random(1,7,1);
$b = $a + $c;
$b1 = -1/($b);

BEGIN_TEXT

Suppose that \[\frac{$a}{($b + x)}  =
 \sum_{n=0}^\infty c_n x^n \] $BR
Find the following coefficients of the power series. $BR
\( c_0 = \) \{ans_rule(20)\}  $BR

\( c_1 = \) \{ans_rule(20)\}  $BR

\( c_2 = \) \{ans_rule(20)\}  $BR

\( c_3 = \) \{ans_rule(20)\}  $BR

\( c_4 = \) \{ans_rule(20)\}  $BR$BR

Find the radius of convergence \( R \) of the power series. $BR
\( R = \)  \{ans_rule(20)\}  . $BR

END_TEXT

$ans0 =  "-$a * $b1" ;
$ans1 =  "$ans0 * $b1" ;
$ans2 =  "$ans1 * $b1" ;
$ans3 =  "$ans2 * $b1" ;
$ans4 =  "$ans3 * $b1" ;
$ans5 =  $b ;


ANS(num_cmp($ans0) );
ANS(num_cmp($ans1) );
ANS(num_cmp($ans2) );
ANS(num_cmp($ans3) );
ANS(num_cmp($ans4) );
ANS(num_cmp($ans5) );

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
